org.apache.cocoon.caching
Class ComponentCacheKey

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.apache.cocoon.caching.ComponentCacheKey
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public final class ComponentCacheKey
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This is the cache key for one sitemap component. It consists of two parts:
a.) The component identifier - a unique handle for the sitemap component
b.) The cache key - a key, generated by the component, which is unique inside the component space.
